23:19.092 --> 23:20.547
No.

23:20.989 --> 23:22.617
You want to see the scar?

23:23.202 --> 23:25.076
What, here? No,
thank you.

23:29.009 --> 23:32.367
I'm sorry about Fiona. She's
got kids. Needs to be up early.

23:32.709 --> 23:34.383
I've got kids, too, so...

23:34.582 --> 23:36.742
What about you, Neil? Children?

23:36.851 --> 23:38.828
No chance. Uh-uh.

23:40.107 --> 23:46.734
No, I value sleep,
time, happiness, style.

23:47.539 --> 23:51.625
- You don't like responsibility.
- Not particularly.

23:52.414 --> 23:56.242
