29:47.543 --> 29:49.152
I dunno.

29:49.285 --> 29:50.774
Has he threatened him?

29:51.011 --> 29:52.540
Don't think so.

29:52.678 --> 29:56.165
He's been to the doctor's.
Because he's not sleeping, apparently.

29:56.423 --> 29:59.079
- Do you know why?
- No.

29:59.423 --> 30:01.641
