- Seriously.

35:32.949 --> 35:34.029
Oh.

35:34.204 --> 35:37.701
Oh, OK. Seriously.

35:38.993 --> 35:42.889
There is nothing
I want more than to...

35:49.085 --> 35:51.975
It's not the offer.
It's the context.

35:52.149 --> 35:53.546
Context!

35:53.725 --> 35:55.639
- God, I love that!
- What?

35:55.756 --> 35:58.248
Just how you talk.

36:02.285 --> 36:04.107
Want to come back to mine?

36:04.826 --> 36:07.873
What? No! This is good.

36:08.840 --> 36:12.303
Look, maybe we should, er,
maybe we should call it a night?

36:12.600 --> 36:14.014
OK...

36:14.850 --> 36:17.394
Doesn't like sex in weird places.

36:20.803 --> 36:23.074
You go home, if you want to.

36:25.416 --> 36:27.005
You'll be all right?

36:27.199 --> 36:28.456
Yeah...

36:29.479 --> 36:31.638
I'll be amazing.

36:32.818 --> 36:34.547
Bye.

36:40.802 --> 36:43.091
Breakfast tomorrow, though,
yeah?

36:43.161 --> 36:44.513
Sure.

