37:23.119 --> 37:24.955
God, I'm shitfaced.

37:25.235 --> 37:27.432
I am desperate for another drink

37:27.495 --> 37:30.550
and that's exactly how I want
to feel cos I haven't got a clue

37:30.643 --> 37:33.112
what's going on in
my life at the moment.

37:34.987 --> 37:36.799
I'm also a doctor
who's putting your mate

37:36.847 --> 37:39.221
in the recovery position
so he doesn't die.

37:39.352 --> 37:40.915
You don't look like a doctor.

37:41.243 --> 37:42.518
No white coat.

37:42.703 --> 37:44.252
You're hot.

37:44.827 --> 37:46.860
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

37:47.320 --> 37:48.819
You think I'm hot?

37:49.847 --> 37:53.636
- Yeah, why not?
- Yeah? You want to suck me off?

37:55.955 --> 37:58.052
- Do you want to fuck me?
- Yeah.

37:58.535 --> 38:00.245
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

38:03.997 --> 38:05.909
Then it's not your night.

38:06.292 --> 38:08.235
- What?
- Take him home.

38:30.867 --> 38:32.316
Simon?

38:37.062 --> 38:38.471
Simon!

38:46.967 --> 38:48.466
I know some...

38:53.151 --> 38:55.146
I'm going to tell you something.

39:43.107 --> 39:46.540
- Hi.
- Had a good night?

39:47.537 --> 39:52.506
Simon's done something, and now
apparently my son doesn't love me.

39:54.727 --> 39:56.389
Neil not back?

39:56.660 --> 39:58.973
He won't be now. It's too late.

39:59.201 --> 40:01.733
- Oh, you mean...
- He'll stay out.

40:02.909 --> 40:04.209
I thought you'd agreed

40:04.326 --> 40:06.497
- he wasn't going to do that any more.
- We did.

40:08.693 --> 40:12.216
- I hope you got what you needed.
- Anna...

40:15.410 --> 40:16.519
are you all right?

40:16.567 --> 40:17.926
I'm going to stay up for a bit,

40:17.974 --> 40:20.410
- do a few things.
- What things?

40:20.583 --> 40:21.966
Big things.

40:24.403 --> 40:25.895
Go to bed.

42:06.507 --> 42:08.426
Shit...

42:13.257 --> 42:15.658
Hello, I'm Nigel from
Golding and Golding.

42:15.744 --> 42:18.336
I believe your husband called
us about a valuation on your...

42:43.717 --> 42:45.259
Well, you were never going
to make it to the café.

42:45.306 --> 42:48.269
So I thought I'd deliver.
Croissants, fruits.

42:48.359 --> 42:51.078
Could only find one
yoghurt. But we could share?

42:59.567 --> 43:00.871
Erm...

43:01.077 --> 43:03.597
