make an excuse and run away,

45:20.733 --> 45:22.650
and count themselves lucky.

45:22.972 --> 45:24.996
You really don't have
to stay out of concern.

45:25.044 --> 45:26.199
Change to what?

45:26.251 --> 45:29.058
- I... I beg your pardon?
- Because things have changed.

45:29.267 --> 45:32.320
Your husband's come back.
Your son's moved out.

45:32.527 --> 45:34.199
