45:34.246 --> 45:36.707
You try and ignore it?
Or change?

45:38.339 --> 45:40.136
What are you, like, a guru?

45:40.218 --> 45:43.481
I'm a teacher. We're pretty
good at giving clear guidance,

45:43.542 --> 45:45.628
- when required.
- Oh, fuck you.

45:45.827 --> 45:47.251
I would like that.

45:48.503 --> 45:50.102
But not for money.

46:25.695 --> 46:28.224
That might be the best I've ever had.

46:30.602 --> 46:32.011
How about you?

46:34.235 --> 46:36.344
Yeah, it was good.

47:09.021 --> 47:10.660
Oh, God.

47:16.665 --> 47:18.164
So... er...

47:20.278 --> 47:23.647
Yeah, er, believe it or not,
he's... he's made the money.

47:24.915 --> 47:26.602
Been very lucky by the sounds of it.

47:26.883 --> 47:30.990
Kate's dad gave them
an amount, erm, he put it in

47:31.038 --> 47:33.491
some American investment,
fracking, apparently.

47:33.675 --> 47:35.508
Ah, he used the dividend
to fund the house,

47:35.556 --> 47:36.939
to borrow against for the business.

47:36.986 --> 47:40.922
His business partner called Mark,
who runs it with him. And then I...

47:43.743 --> 47:46.688
I couldn't find out anything
more about Tom or why...

47:48.110 --> 47:49.334
Or why...

47:52.212 --> 47:53.711
Neil.

47:58.403 --> 47:59.952
Neil.

48:06.245 --> 48:10.578
When I got back this morning,
erm, she packed a bag for me.

48:10.670 --> 48:12.879
Said it was over.
We'd made a commitment to each other,

48:13.003 --> 48:19.157
I'd failed. She'd... she'd sort
my stuff and... and send it on.

48:26.994 --> 48:30.133
I shouldn't have gone last night.
It's not your fault.

48:37.780 --> 48:39.519
I don't know where I'm going to go.

48:39.643 --> 48:41.197
You stay at mine.

48:43.001 --> 48:44.690
I don't think that would help much.

48:46.711 --> 48:50.320
Anyway I'm, er, I'm used to a hotel.

48:52.005 --> 48:56.794
- She will get over this.
- She won't. Not now.

48:59.515 --> 49:02.603
Sorry. Anyway, so that's,
erm, all I could find out.

49:02.651 --> 49:04.544
No, it's useful.

49:06.811 --> 49:08.550
Thank you.

49:11.134 --> 49:13.756
Simon hates you.

49:19.715 --> 49:23.006
Hates me, too. He knew what
he was doing last night.

49:23.181 --> 49:24.725
He got me drunk and

49:25.460 --> 49:27.741
when I woke up this morning
and realised what had happened

49:29.037 --> 49:31.639
I knew she'd never forgive me again.

49:39.108 --> 49:42.708
But, yeah, he hates you
