49:43.538 --> 49:45.038
Someone's talking to him.

49:45.295 --> 49:47.774
Is there anyone you don't trust?

49:49.818 --> 49:53.901
The headache's still there.
Have you had the blood test back?

49:55.110 --> 49:57.668
